{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073330/extras/Steam_Page_GIF_Text_The_Perfect_Blend_English.png?t=1737092061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073330/extras/SteamGIF_Overview.gif?t=1737092061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">SillySuspects is an outrageously hilarious first-person detective game with a comedic twist on the murder mystery genre. With its blend of humour, intrigue, and endless possibilities, SillySuspects promises an experience like no other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the detective, you\u2019ll dive head first into a dynamically generated world teeming with quirky characters, each with their own lives, secrets and motives. Your mission? Uncover the identity of the crafty criminal by exploring vibrant cities, analysing bizarre crime scenes, and investigating quirky characters to unravel a wild and wacky mystery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready to bring justice to this hilariously chaotic world?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073330/extras/Steam_Page_GIF_Text_Navigate_A_Uniquely_Generated_City_English.png?t=1737092061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073330/extras/SteamGIF_Navigate_A_Uniquely_Generated_City.gif?t=1737092061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each crime case is in a different location; it\u2019s up to you to learn the layout of the land to be successful in the investigative journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073330/extras/Steam_Page_GIF_Text_Analyse_Bizare_Crime_Scenes_English.png?t=1737092061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073330/extras/SteamGIF_Analyse_Bizzare_Crime_Scenes.gif?t=1737092061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is a lot more to a laundry basket, step ladder and frying pan than meets the eye. Scour for clues to discover vital information about the criminal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073330/extras/Steam_Page_GIF_Text_Interview_Quirky_Characters_English.png?t=1737092061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073330/extras/SteamGIF_Interview_Quirky_Characters.gif?t=1737092061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">These whacky, weird and wonderful characters won't always tell you the truth. Determine fact from fiction to unravel the mystery and solve the case.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073330/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737092061","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073330/page.bg.jpg?t=1737092061","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073330/8fc1a7ac2841947d0c6ccf5141112796c05e83f2/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737092061","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073330/8fc1a7ac2841947d0c6ccf5141112796c05e83f2/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737092061","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073330/extras/Steam_Page_GIF_Text_The_Perfect_Blend_English.png?t=1737092061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_it